      "review_summary": "The PR adds a shared managed-proxy-aware app fetch transport, migrates web/media/plugin/skill download callers to it, and retires `tools.web.fetch.useTrustedEnvProxy` plus `tools.web.fetch.ssrfPolicy`.\n\nPR surface: Source +398, Tests +784, Docs +6. Total +1188 across 51 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. from source with high confidence: the new tests explicitly exercise successful localhost/private app fetches, and the transport only detects managed-proxy activation rather than requiring it. No live execution was needed to establish the changed policy semantics.",
